  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the response to chemotherapy in breast cancer patients by the use of
      Diffusion-weighted magnetic resonance imaging of the breast before the start of chemotherapy,
      after one and 3 cycles of therapy and at the end of the therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
